@startuml AuraBeauty_Sequence_Menjalankan_Analisis

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #424242
    ActorBorderColor #E65100
    ParticipantBorderColor #1565C0
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #E3F2FD
    LifeLineBorderColor #90A4AE
    LifeLineBackgroundColor #ECEFF1
}

title AuraBeauty BI - Diagram Sekuen\nMenjalankan Analisis Apriori

actor "Analis Data" as User
participant "Browser" as Browser
participant "Laravel\nRouter" as Router
participant "Analytics\nController" as Controller
participant "Process\nFacade" as Process
participant "Skrip\nPython Apriori" as Python
participant "Berkas CSV\n(produk & transaksi)" as CSV
participant "association_rules.csv" as RulesCSV

User -> Browser : Klik tombol "Run Analysis"
Browser -> Router : POST /analytics/apriori/run
Router -> Controller : runAnalysis()

Controller -> Controller : Menentukan jalur skrip
Controller -> Controller : Mendeteksi eksekusi python

Controller -> Process : run("python scripts/apriori_analysis.py")
Process -> Python : Eksekusi skrip

Python -> CSV : Baca product_code Sheet1.csv
Python -> CSV : Baca transactions Sheet1.csv
Python -> Python : Bersihkan spasi
Python -> Python : Pemetaan product_code → product_name
Python -> Python : Kelompokkan berdasarkan customer_id
Python -> Python : Saring pelanggan dengan >1 item

alt mlxtend terinstal
    Python -> Python : TransactionEncoder.fit_transform()
    Python -> Python : apriori(min_support=0.015)
    Python -> Python : association_rules(metric=confidence)
else mlxtend tidak terinstal
    Python -> Python : Hitung 1-itemset
    Python -> Python : Hitung 2-itemset
    Python -> Python : Hasilkan aturan confidence & lift
end

Python -> Python : Urutkan aturan berdasarkan lift, confidence
Python -> RulesCSV : Tulis association_rules.csv
Python --> Process : Kembalikan kode keluar 0 + stdout
Process --> Controller : successful()

Controller -> Controller : Catat log sukses
Controller -> Router : Redirect /analytics/apriori
Router -> Browser : 302 + pesan sukses
Browser -> User : Tampilkan pesan sukses

@enduml